DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    VALUES('clientes'[Sexo])

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'clientes'[Sexo], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
  'clientes'[Sexo]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"Feminino"}, 'clientes'[Sexo])

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('clientes'[Sexo], __DS0FilterTable, "SumSaldo", CALCULATE(SUM('clientes'[Saldo])))

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [SumSaldo], 0, 'clientes'[Sexo], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
  [SumSaldo] DESC, 'clientes'[Sexo]
